column5: I'm thinking of heading out in the morning tomorrow for the some trout - resident, steelies...haven't really decided yet.  If anyone is interested, let me know.  I want to go between 7 and 12.
PM me where you would want to meet and if I can I'll get out with ya. geoff
going to the credit tmro in the morning
Heyif you guys are looking for one more let me know....i have an open day tomorrow and would love to catch a trout or two.
I will be there first thing in the morning at first light. Hope to see you there Jose

Hey guys,  Was out trout fishing today. The wife had some running around to do... so the minute she left I snuck down to the river for an hour. Landed 3 lost 1. Water was cool, clear and sun was shining a good day of steelheading!  I am unable to start my own post because i am fairly new but wanted to post some fish porn.  Enjoy.
Nice fish porn we always love the fish porn
nice report   i always wanted to catch a rainbow on crankies....never tried tho..

Hey Newboykool,  This year I have had a few good days for bows... all on husky jerks, or crayfish lures, bright orange, silver or pink.  I never use roe always inline spinners of the above lures.   Toss, hook set and hold on my friend.  Chad
thanks guess i'll be bringing a fly rod and a bait caster tmro
Nice The first one looks very healthy
